00:00:01.170 --> 00:00:04.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[explosion]
[rumbling]</b></Default>

c0000001
00:00:06.760 --> 00:00:07.680 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FERN]
I see now.</b></Default>

c0000002
00:00:07.760 --> 00:00:09.680 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Your training is what
made this fissure.</b></Default>

c0000003
00:01:52.190 --> 00:01:53.940 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000004
00:01:54.030 --> 00:01:56.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But if you don't intend
to fight the dragon,</b></Default>

c0000005
00:01:57.250 --> 00:01:59.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>why do you continue to train?</b></Default>

c0000006
00:02:01.370 --> 00:02:02.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[STARK] When I first
got to this village,</b></Default>

c0000007
00:02:03.580 --> 00:02:05.050 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>its people were living in fear.</b></Default>

c0000008
00:02:05.760 --> 00:02:07.590 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hard not to
with a dragon nearby.</b></Default>

c0000009
00:02:08.840 --> 00:02:10.050 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Now they're all smiles.</b></Default>

c0000010
00:02:11.050 --> 00:02:13.010 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>They're convinced
that as long as I'm around,</b></Default>

c0000011
00:02:13.670 --> 00:02:16.520 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>their home remains safe
from another brutal attack.</b></Default>

c0000012
00:02:18.020 --> 00:02:20.020 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Even though
I haven't done a damn thing.</b></Default>

c0000013
00:02:21.310 --> 00:02:23.770 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The only reason the dragon
hasn't destroyed this place</b></Default>

c0000014
00:02:24.060 --> 00:02:25.570 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>is because it hasn't
felt like it.</b></Default>

c0000015
00:02:25.690 --> 00:02:29.280 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000016
00:02:31.280 --> 00:02:33.190 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What if it does feel like it?</b></Default>

c0000017
00:02:33.730 --> 00:02:35.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Will you fight it
if there's no other choice?</b></Default>

c0000018
00:02:36.120 --> 00:02:37.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[STARK]
I'm not keen on dying,</b></Default>

c0000019
00:02:38.040 --> 00:02:39.490 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but that's a minor thing.</b></Default>

c0000020
00:02:40.290 --> 00:02:43.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I have a title to uphold
and people to protect.</b></Default>

c0000021
00:02:44.960 --> 00:02:47.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm Stark,
the hero of this village.</b></Default>

c0000022
00:02:48.050 --> 00:02:49.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And it's my job to defend it.</b></Default>

c0000023
00:02:49.880 --> 00:02:52.050 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000024
00:02:52.130 --> 00:02:53.800 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[scoffs]
Easy to say that now,</b></Default>

c0000025
00:02:54.420 --> 00:02:56.890 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but knowing myself,
I'll run away.</b></Default>

c0000026
00:03:00.260 --> 00:03:01.640 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>This scar on my forehead?</b></Default>

c0000027
00:03:02.600 --> 00:03:04.310 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I didn't get it
taking on a monster.</b></Default>

c0000028
00:03:04.900 --> 00:03:06.900 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's from a fight
I had with my master.</b></Default>

c0000029
00:03:07.480 --> 00:03:08.480 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[explosion]</b></Default>

c0000030
00:03:08.570 --> 00:03:09.570 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[thudding]</b></Default>

c0000031
00:03:11.940 --> 00:03:13.610 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[STARK] It was the first time
he ever hit me.</b></Default>

c0000032
00:03:16.700 --> 00:03:18.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>He must've been disappointed.</b></Default>

c0000033
00:03:19.700 --> 00:03:20.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Had to have been.</b></Default>

c0000034
00:03:21.240 --> 00:03:22.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Throughout
our whole relationship,</b></Default>

c0000035
00:03:22.700 --> 00:03:24.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>he never praised me
a single time.</b></Default>

c0000036
00:03:32.750 --> 00:03:33.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What now?</b></Default>

c0000037
00:03:35.300 --> 00:03:36.510 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FERN]
We just met, but...</b></Default>

c0000038
00:03:37.550 --> 00:03:38.890 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I don't think you'll run.</b></Default>

c0000039
00:03:41.510 --> 00:03:42.760 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You don't know me at all.</b></Default>

c0000040
00:03:43.390 --> 00:03:44.470 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FERN]
You're right about that.</b></Default>

c0000041
00:03:45.110 --> 00:03:47.440 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But I have been
in a similar situation.</b></Default>

c0000042
00:03:48.230 --> 00:03:49.270 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>All right. Let's hear it.</b></Default>

c0000043
00:03:50.650 --> 00:03:51.860 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[growling]
-[FERN] The first time</b></Default>

c0000044
00:03:51.940 --> 00:03:53.310 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>that I fought a monster...</b></Default>

c0000045
00:03:54.480 --> 00:03:56.070 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I had trained more than enough,</b></Default>

c0000046
00:03:56.820 --> 00:03:58.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but I was frozen by fear.</b></Default>

c0000047
00:03:59.700 --> 00:04:01.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I couldn't muster the courage
to fight back.</b></Default>

c0000048
00:04:02.990 --> 00:04:04.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>All I could do was run.</b></Default>

c0000049
00:04:05.540 --> 00:04:07.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[roaring]</b></Default>

c0000050
00:04:07.630 --> 00:04:09.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FERN]
It kept on chasing me,</b></Default>

c0000051
00:04:09.960 --> 00:04:12.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and for some reason,
Mistress Frieren wouldn't help.</b></Default>

c0000052
00:04:12.920 --> 00:04:15.050 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[STARK] [chuckles]
My master was like that, too.</b></Default>

c0000053
00:04:15.800 --> 00:04:17.800 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FERN] When it finally
had me cornered,</b></Default>

c0000054
00:04:18.390 --> 00:04:19.890 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I steeled my resolve,</b></Default>

c0000055
00:04:20.800 --> 00:04:22.260 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and instinct took over.</b></Default>

c0000056
00:04:23.090 --> 00:04:25.940 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000057
00:04:27.190 --> 00:04:29.560 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FERN] All that I needed
to do was ground myself.</b></Default>

c0000058
00:04:30.850 --> 00:04:32.850 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Your training
isn't going to fail you.</b></Default>

c0000059
00:04:32.940 --> 00:04:34.190 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Mine didn't fail me.</b></Default>

c0000060
00:04:35.610 --> 00:04:38.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You're a coward hiding
beneath a veneer of bravery,</b></Default>

c0000061
00:04:39.030 --> 00:04:40.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but your resolve
to protect the village?</b></Default>

c0000062
00:04:41.360 --> 00:04:43.860 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That, at least,
I believe is real.</b></Default>

c0000063
00:04:46.250 --> 00:04:49.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[wind whooshing]
-[leaves rustling]</b></Default>

c0000064
00:04:52.870 --> 00:04:53.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[STARK]
My resolve?</b></Default>

c0000065
00:04:55.050 --> 00:04:56.050 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Huh.</b></Default>

c0000066
00:04:57.300 --> 00:04:59.220 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[door opens and closes]</b></Default>

c0000067
00:05:02.260 --> 00:05:03.340 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN]
How did it go?</b></Default>

c0000068
00:05:05.100 --> 00:05:06.520 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FERN]
I don't know for sure.</b></Default>

c0000069
00:05:07.640 --> 00:05:09.060 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But if I had to guess...</b></Default>

c0000070
00:05:11.350 --> 00:05:13.310 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I think it'll turn out
all right.</b></Default>

c0000071
00:05:16.820 --> 00:05:19.820 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[birds chirping]</b></Default>

c0000072
00:05:23.650 --> 00:05:25.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-He ran, then.
-That's a shame.</b></Default>

c0000073
00:05:26.410 --> 00:05:28.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I had high hopes for the lad.</b></Default>

c0000074
00:05:28.750 --> 00:05:30.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN]
We're left with no choice.</b></Default>

c0000075
00:05:30.290 --> 00:05:32.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Prepare yourself
for dragon-sized tag.</b></Default>

c0000076
00:05:32.540 --> 00:05:33.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Huh?</b></Default>

c0000077
00:05:35.670 --> 00:05:36.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[grunts]</b></Default>

c0000078
00:05:37.050 --> 00:05:38.050 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[STARK] Frieren.
-Hm?</b></Default>

c0000079
00:05:40.590 --> 00:05:42.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You only need
30 seconds, right?</b></Default>

c0000080
00:05:44.130 --> 00:05:45.310 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You took your time.</b></Default>

c0000081
00:05:46.520 --> 00:05:48.230 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I want you to promise me
one thing.</b></Default>

c0000082
00:05:48.730 --> 00:05:50.390 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If I die fighting this dragon,</b></Default>

c0000083
00:05:50.980 --> 00:05:52.600 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>you have to finish it off
for me.</b></Default>

c0000084
00:05:54.020 --> 00:05:54.940 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>All right.</b></Default>

c0000085
00:05:55.360 --> 00:05:56.320 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I promise.</b></Default>

c0000086
00:05:57.320 --> 00:06:00.780 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But why would you sacrifice
so much for the townsfolk?</b></Default>

c0000087
00:06:02.940 --> 00:06:04.320 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[chuckles]
-What?</b></Default>

c0000088
00:06:04.820 --> 00:06:05.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Just...</b></Default>

c0000089
00:06:06.000 --> 00:06:07.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>that's kind of an odd question.</b></Default>

c0000090
00:06:08.790 --> 00:06:10.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I've lived here
for three whole years now.</b></Default>

c0000091
00:06:14.120 --> 00:06:16.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[FRIEREN] Not long.
-[STARK] Yes, long.</b></Default>

c0000092
00:06:17.460 --> 00:06:19.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[growling]</b></Default>

c0000093
00:06:20.510 --> 00:06:22.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[STARK]
Okay. Let's get to business.</b></Default>

c0000094
00:06:23.800 --> 00:06:25.270 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Your hands are shaking.</b></Default>

c0000095
00:06:25.850 --> 00:06:27.640 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm scared.
What do you expect?</b></Default>

c0000096
00:06:28.520 --> 00:06:29.520 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[chuckles]</b></Default>

c0000097
00:06:30.060 --> 00:06:31.270 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[STARK]
Is something funny to you?</b></Default>

c0000098
00:06:32.270 --> 00:06:33.890 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You're exactly like Eisen.</b></Default>

c0000099
00:06:34.020 --> 00:06:35.820 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[fluttering]
-[STARK] I am?</b></Default>

c0000100
00:06:37.150 --> 00:06:38.730 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[HIMMEL]
This is a powerful foe.</b></Default>

c0000101
00:06:40.110 --> 00:06:42.280 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But your hands.
They're out of control.</b></Default>

c0000102
00:06:42.530 --> 00:06:43.400 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You afraid?</b></Default>

c0000103
00:06:44.570 --> 00:06:45.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[EISEN]
Yes.</b></Default>

c0000104
00:06:46.120 --> 00:06:47.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN] Didn't take much
to get that out of you.</b></Default>

c0000105
00:06:49.040 --> 00:06:51.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[EISEN] Being afraid
isn't a bad thing.</b></Default>

c0000106
00:06:53.160 --> 00:06:54.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Without fear,</b></Default>

c0000107
00:06:55.250 --> 00:06:57.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I wouldn't have
made it this far.</b></Default>

c0000108
00:06:57.300 --> 00:07:00.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000109
00:07:00.800 --> 00:07:02.840 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Even the way
they tremble's the same.</b></Default>

c0000110
00:07:08.680 --> 00:07:09.720 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[STARK]
I get it now.</b></Default>

c0000111
00:07:09.850 --> 00:07:12.390 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000112
00:07:14.350 --> 00:07:15.360 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[STARK]
My master?</b></Default>

c0000113
00:07:16.820 --> 00:07:17.940 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>He was afraid, too.</b></Default>

c0000114
00:07:19.480 --> 00:07:22.980 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>All I have to do
is steel my resolve.</b></Default>

c0000115
00:07:23.110 --> 00:07:24.940 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000116
00:07:27.450 --> 00:07:29.030 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN] He's entered
the dragon's range.</b></Default>

c0000117
00:07:30.370 --> 00:07:31.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Why isn't it attacking him?</b></Default>

c0000118
00:07:33.200 --> 00:07:34.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN]
It knows better.</b></Default>

c0000119
00:07:35.840 --> 00:07:36.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I thought so.</b></Default>

c0000120
00:07:37.960 --> 00:07:39.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[inhales sharply]</b></Default>

c0000121
00:07:40.500 --> 00:07:41.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[growling]</b></Default>

c0000122
00:07:42.290 --> 00:07:43.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[roaring]</b></Default>

c0000123
00:07:45.010 --> 00:07:46.300 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[explosion]
-[FRIEREN] No wonder</b></Default>

c0000124
00:07:46.390 --> 00:07:47.800 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>it left the village alone.</b></Default>

c0000125
00:07:49.050 --> 00:07:51.010 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Dragons are smart creatures.</b></Default>

c0000126
00:07:51.800 --> 00:07:53.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>They're not foolish enough
to pick a fight</b></Default>

c0000127
00:07:53.640 --> 00:07:55.440 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>against a powerful opponent.</b></Default>

c0000128
00:07:57.900 --> 00:08:00.400 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Eisen didn't hit Stark
for being weak</b></Default>

c0000129
00:08:00.940 --> 00:08:02.980 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>or because he was
disappointed in him.</b></Default>

c0000130
00:08:04.150 --> 00:08:05.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's much simpler than that.</b></Default>

c0000131
00:08:05.740 --> 00:08:07.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000132
00:08:11.070 --> 00:08:13.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[EISEN]
The two of us parted in anger.</b></Default>

c0000133
00:08:13.910 --> 00:08:15.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[fire crackling]
-[FRIEREN] You hit him?</b></Default>

c0000134
00:08:18.460 --> 00:08:20.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[EISEN]
My body moved on its own.</b></Default>

c0000135
00:08:21.130 --> 00:08:22.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I feel terrible.</b></Default>

c0000136
00:08:23.210 --> 00:08:25.390 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm forever sorry
for what I did.</b></Default>

c0000137
00:08:25.470 --> 00:08:27.340 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[fire crackling]</b></Default>

c0000138
00:08:27.470 --> 00:08:28.800 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[EISEN]
I was afraid.</b></Default>

c0000139
00:08:30.140 --> 00:08:32.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I was afraid
of the boy, Frieren.</b></Default>

c0000140
00:08:34.970 --> 00:08:36.980 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I couldn't believe his power.</b></Default>

c0000141
00:08:38.350 --> 00:08:39.560 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>My apprentice</b></Default>

c0000142
00:08:40.230 --> 00:08:42.350 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>will become a great warrior.</b></Default>

c0000143
00:08:44.270 --> 00:08:45.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[thudding]</b></Default>

c0000144
00:08:45.320 --> 00:08:47.070 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[rumbling]</b></Default>

c0000145
00:08:47.160 --> 00:08:49.070 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000146
00:08:53.030 --> 00:08:54.240 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[grunting]</b></Default>

c0000147
00:08:56.040 --> 00:08:57.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000148
00:09:01.830 --> 00:09:02.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[grunts]</b></Default>

c0000149
00:09:03.960 --> 00:09:05.090 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[roaring]</b></Default>

c0000150
00:09:05.300 --> 00:09:07.010 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000151
00:09:11.050 --> 00:09:14.050 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[explosions]</b></Default>

c0000152
00:09:17.560 --> 00:09:19.560 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Now! Let him have it!</b></Default>

c0000153
00:09:23.270 --> 00:09:25.360 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hey! Shoot it already!</b></Default>

c0000154
00:09:25.820 --> 00:09:27.740 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I did exactly
what you told me to!</b></Default>

c0000155
00:09:28.030 --> 00:09:29.650 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You expect me
to kill it myself?</b></Default>

c0000156
00:09:29.860 --> 00:09:31.610 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You can't be serious, old hag!</b></Default>

c0000157
00:09:31.860 --> 00:09:33.400 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yeah, you're just like
my master after all!</b></Default>

c0000158
00:09:33.490 --> 00:09:34.860 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's already dead.</b></Default>

c0000159
00:09:35.580 --> 00:09:36.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Huh?</b></Default>

c0000160
00:09:37.710 --> 00:09:38.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>"Old hag," huh?</b></Default>

c0000161
00:09:40.120 --> 00:09:41.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FERN]
He'll live to regret that.</b></Default>

c0000162
00:09:42.660 --> 00:09:45.470 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000163
00:09:45.590 --> 00:09:46.590 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[STARK]
I killed it...</b></Default>

c0000164
00:09:47.720 --> 00:09:48.720 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>on my own?</b></Default>

c0000165
00:09:50.090 --> 00:09:51.720 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I didn't need any help.</b></Default>

c0000166
00:09:53.220 --> 00:09:54.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I beat the dragon.</b></Default>

c0000167
00:09:56.810 --> 00:09:57.810 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN]
Good work.</b></Default>

c0000168
00:09:58.730 --> 00:09:59.890 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You were exceptional.</b></Default>

c0000169
00:10:00.520 --> 00:10:01.850 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That was quite the show.</b></Default>

c0000170
00:10:02.640 --> 00:10:03.560 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Well done.</b></Default>

c0000171
00:10:06.400 --> 00:10:08.780 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪ Now this horde
of treasure is mine! ♪</b></Default>

c0000172
00:10:08.940 --> 00:10:10.030 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-At last!
-[FERN] We can't take it</b></Default>

c0000173
00:10:10.110 --> 00:10:11.280 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>all with us.</b></Default>

c0000174
00:10:11.650 --> 00:10:13.820 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[wind whooshing]</b></Default>

c0000175
00:10:14.280 --> 00:10:15.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[chuckles]</b></Default>

c0000176
00:10:16.200 --> 00:10:18.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[Frieren grunts]
-[FERN] Three items only.</b></Default>

c0000177
00:10:18.830 --> 00:10:20.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[Frieren grunts]
-Hm.</b></Default>

c0000178
00:10:20.500 --> 00:10:21.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[clattering]
-[gasps]</b></Default>

c0000179
00:10:22.500 --> 00:10:24.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Does this not feel
silly to you?</b></Default>

c0000180
00:10:24.870 --> 00:10:26.840 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You're really interested
in this old junk?</b></Default>

c0000181
00:10:26.920 --> 00:10:28.590 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN]
This junk is treasure.</b></Default>

c0000182
00:10:29.420 --> 00:10:30.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[STARK]
My master always told me</b></Default>

c0000183
00:10:31.590 --> 00:10:33.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>that you made
the heroes' adventure</b></Default>

c0000184
00:10:33.210 --> 00:10:34.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>a ridiculous one.</b></Default>

c0000185
00:10:35.430 --> 00:10:36.430 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN]
Oh?</b></Default>

c0000186
00:10:37.100 --> 00:10:38.100 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>In a good way.</b></Default>

c0000187
00:10:38.890 --> 00:10:41.140 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I guess your silliness
made things fun.</b></Default>

c0000188
00:10:41.270 --> 00:10:42.810 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[clanking]</b></Default>

c0000189
00:10:43.020 --> 00:10:45.730 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000190
00:10:45.900 --> 00:10:46.940 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[HEITER]
Incredible!</b></Default>

c0000191
00:10:47.070 --> 00:10:48.940 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You actually made shaved ice!</b></Default>

c0000192
00:10:49.030 --> 00:10:51.730 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN] [chuckles] I told you
this spell was worth it.</b></Default>

c0000193
00:10:51.900 --> 00:10:53.150 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[HEITER] I would take on armies</b></Default>

c0000194
00:10:53.230 --> 00:10:54.940 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to experience such fluffiness!</b></Default>

c0000195
00:10:55.030 --> 00:10:55.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN]
Rightly so.</b></Default>

c0000196
00:10:56.370 --> 00:10:57.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[EISEN]
This is ridiculous.</b></Default>

c0000197
00:10:58.160 --> 00:10:59.740 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We're wasting our time.</b></Default>

c0000198
00:11:00.240 --> 00:11:01.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We have time to spare.</b></Default>

c0000199
00:11:02.040 --> 00:11:04.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Our journey has only
just begun, after all.</b></Default>

c0000200
00:11:05.300 --> 00:11:06.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[EISEN]
The Hero of the South</b></Default>

c0000201
00:11:06.500 --> 00:11:08.300 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>was said to be
our strongest weapon.</b></Default>

c0000202
00:11:08.840 --> 00:11:11.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The Seven Sages of Destruction
slaughtered him.</b></Default>

c0000203
00:11:12.840 --> 00:11:14.090 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The four of us</b></Default>

c0000204
00:11:14.670 --> 00:11:16.850 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>may well not
make it back alive.</b></Default>

c0000205
00:11:18.260 --> 00:11:19.350 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So, what then?</b></Default>

c0000206
00:11:19.560 --> 00:11:21.760 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Want your last journey
to be painful and hard?</b></Default>

c0000207
00:11:21.930 --> 00:11:25.010 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000208
00:11:25.100 --> 00:11:26.110 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[HIMMEL]
That's no fun.</b></Default>

c0000209
00:11:26.570 --> 00:11:28.520 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If you ask me about it,
I would take</b></Default>

c0000210
00:11:28.610 --> 00:11:30.650 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>the more lighthearted journey
any day.</b></Default>

c0000211
00:11:31.150 --> 00:11:32.770 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>One I can laugh about
at the end.</b></Default>

c0000212
00:11:32.860 --> 00:11:35.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000213
00:11:36.030 --> 00:11:37.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Just the warmth of a finger,</b></Default>

c0000214
00:11:37.660 --> 00:11:39.490 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and it melts
almost instantaneously!</b></Default>

c0000215
00:11:39.580 --> 00:11:41.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Please keep your fingers
away from our food.</b></Default>

c0000216
00:11:41.410 --> 00:11:42.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[EISEN]
Ridiculous.</b></Default>

c0000217
00:11:42.830 --> 00:11:45.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[HEITER] Oh, and what do
we do about the syrup?</b></Default>

c0000218
00:11:45.420 --> 00:11:47.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN] I don't have
a spell to produce that.</b></Default>

c0000219
00:11:47.590 --> 00:11:48.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[HIMMEL]
Really?</b></Default>

c0000220
00:11:48.540 --> 00:11:50.590 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[EISEN]
Even more ridiculous.</b></Default>

c0000221
00:11:51.630 --> 00:11:53.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000222
00:12:05.310 --> 00:12:07.400 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN] Well?
Can you see through them?</b></Default>

c0000223
00:12:07.980 --> 00:12:09.020 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FERN]
Yes, but...</b></Default>

c0000224
00:12:09.770 --> 00:12:12.230 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I can't say I find
this spell interesting.</b></Default>

c0000225
00:12:12.310 --> 00:12:15.020 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm so sorry my body
isn't interesting to you.</b></Default>

c0000226
00:12:15.110 --> 00:12:16.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[birds chirping]</b></Default>

c0000227
00:12:16.530 --> 00:12:17.530 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hm?</b></Default>

c0000228
00:12:17.950 --> 00:12:18.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What?</b></Default>

c0000229
00:12:20.030 --> 00:12:22.240 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-So small.
-[STARK] No part of me's small!</b></Default>

c0000230
00:12:23.120 --> 00:12:23.990 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Well, Stark.</b></Default>

c0000231
00:12:24.570 --> 00:12:26.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Where will your journey
lead you next?</b></Default>

c0000232
00:12:27.040 --> 00:12:29.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I suppose you could make
your way back to Eisen now.</b></Default>

c0000233
00:12:30.330 --> 00:12:32.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Didn't my master tell you
to take me with you?</b></Default>

c0000234
00:12:33.830 --> 00:12:34.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Besides...</b></Default>

c0000235
00:12:36.430 --> 00:12:38.050 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'd like to have
a ridiculous adventure</b></Default>

c0000236
00:12:38.140 --> 00:12:39.260 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>or two of my own.</b></Default>

c0000237
00:12:40.680 --> 00:12:42.220 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[birds fluttering]</b></Default>

c0000238
00:12:44.800 --> 00:12:45.980 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000239
00:12:49.980 --> 00:12:51.100 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[fire crackling]</b></Default>

c0000240
00:12:51.190 --> 00:12:52.600 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MALE GUARD CAPTAIN 5A]
There is monster activity</b></Default>

c0000241
00:12:52.690 --> 00:12:53.940 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>in the northern lands.</b></Default>

c0000242
00:12:54.400 --> 00:12:55.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>At this time,</b></Default>

c0000243
00:12:55.660 --> 00:12:57.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>no one can pass
through the checkpoint.</b></Default>

c0000244
00:12:59.320 --> 00:13:00.860 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Well, at what time can we?</b></Default>

c0000245
00:13:01.110 --> 00:13:02.610 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It has to open some day.</b></Default>

c0000246
00:13:03.490 --> 00:13:04.360 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Does it?</b></Default>

c0000247
00:13:04.610 --> 00:13:07.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It hasn't since
I was very first posted here.</b></Default>

c0000248
00:13:07.460 --> 00:13:10.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>After all, no people out
means no monsters in.</b></Default>

c0000249
00:13:12.420 --> 00:13:13.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[MALE GUARD 6A] Pardon me.
-[gasps]</b></Default>

c0000250
00:13:14.460 --> 00:13:16.220 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The castellan would like
to see you, sir.</b></Default>

c0000251
00:13:17.220 --> 00:13:18.220 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MALE GUARD CAPTAIN 5A]
Be right there.</b></Default>

c0000252
00:13:19.510 --> 00:13:21.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Listen close, adventurers.</b></Default>

c0000253
00:13:22.130 --> 00:13:25.300 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You would be wise not to cause
any trouble in this town.</b></Default>

c0000254
00:13:26.600 --> 00:13:29.060 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[footsteps]</b></Default>

c0000255
00:13:30.640 --> 00:13:32.600 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FERN] That wasn't
a very warm welcome.</b></Default>

c0000256
00:13:32.980 --> 00:13:34.100 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN]
He's a good guard.</b></Default>

c0000257
00:13:34.350 --> 00:13:35.900 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Wants to keep his people safe,</b></Default>

c0000258
00:13:36.570 --> 00:13:38.820 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and is appropriately harsh
on outsiders,</b></Default>

c0000259
00:13:39.450 --> 00:13:42.030 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>as every proper town guard
ought to be in my opinion.</b></Default>

c0000260
00:13:43.360 --> 00:13:44.610 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[indistinct chatter]
-Hmm...</b></Default>

c0000261
00:13:45.870 --> 00:13:47.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN] Speaking of safety,</b></Default>

c0000262
00:13:48.120 --> 00:13:50.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>this city seems
to have it in spades.</b></Default>

c0000263
00:13:50.210 --> 00:13:52.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Which is a positive
of being stuck here.</b></Default>

c0000264
00:13:53.620 --> 00:13:55.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>This is the perfect time
to slow down</b></Default>

c0000265
00:13:55.510 --> 00:13:56.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and study our craft.</b></Default>

c0000266
00:13:56.920 --> 00:14:00.050 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Once we drop off our things,
the magic shops are all mine.</b></Default>

c0000267
00:14:03.840 --> 00:14:04.800 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Come now.</b></Default>

c0000268
00:14:04.970 --> 00:14:06.270 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The checkpoint is locked tight.</b></Default>

c0000269
00:14:06.350 --> 00:14:07.600 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We have no other choice.</b></Default>

c0000270
00:14:08.770 --> 00:14:10.350 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Run along.
You're free to roam.</b></Default>

c0000271
00:14:10.770 --> 00:14:12.270 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'll secure us a room
at the inn.</b></Default>

c0000272
00:14:15.310 --> 00:14:16.740 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Wanna get something to eat?</b></Default>

c0000273
00:14:18.280 --> 00:14:20.280 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[STARK]
Loud and clear.</b></Default>

c0000274
00:14:21.610 --> 00:14:22.610 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Scary.</b></Default>

c0000275
00:14:24.150 --> 00:14:25.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[indistinct chatter]</b></Default>

c0000276
00:14:28.410 --> 00:14:29.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MALE VILLAGER 6A]
Rumor is they shut down</b></Default>

c0000277
00:14:29.660 --> 00:14:30.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>the sea routes, too.</b></Default>

c0000278
00:14:31.580 --> 00:14:32.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MALE VILLAGER 6B]
The northern lands' army says</b></Default>

c0000279
00:14:33.000 --> 00:14:34.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>they'll take care
of the problem,</b></Default>

c0000280
00:14:34.830 --> 00:14:35.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but I give it two years</b></Default>

c0000281
00:14:36.010 --> 00:14:37.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>until the checkpoint
opens up again.</b></Default>

c0000282
00:14:39.170 --> 00:14:40.840 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Business is at a standstill.</b></Default>

c0000283
00:14:44.550 --> 00:14:46.220 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[STARK]
I haven't had this in forever!</b></Default>

c0000284
00:14:46.930 --> 00:14:48.350 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The jumbo berry special.</b></Default>

c0000285
00:14:49.680 --> 00:14:51.770 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I was just a kid
when I came here last.</b></Default>

c0000286
00:14:52.220 --> 00:14:53.810 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I actually had to split it
with my master</b></Default>

c0000287
00:14:53.890 --> 00:14:55.310 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>'cause I couldn't
finish it alone.</b></Default>

c0000288
00:14:56.820 --> 00:14:59.190 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But, uh, I feel like
this thing has shrunk.</b></Default>

c0000289
00:14:59.900 --> 00:15:00.940 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I would know.</b></Default>

c0000290
00:15:01.230 --> 00:15:02.730 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's the same size as ever.</b></Default>

c0000291
00:15:02.900 --> 00:15:04.030 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You've simply grown up.</b></Default>

c0000292
00:15:05.110 --> 00:15:06.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I suppose...</b></Default>

c0000293
00:15:06.950 --> 00:15:08.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>age does change our perception.</b></Default>

c0000294
00:15:10.160 --> 00:15:12.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Everything seemed huge
when I was a kid.</b></Default>

c0000295
00:15:13.120 --> 00:15:15.800 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I used to think
my master's back was so broad,</b></Default>

c0000296
00:15:16.710 --> 00:15:19.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but even that started
to look small.</b></Default>

c0000297
00:15:20.460 --> 00:15:22.590 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MAN 5A] Eisen is getting up
there in years.</b></Default>

c0000298
00:15:23.050 --> 00:15:24.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I hope you're being
a dutiful student.</b></Default>

c0000299
00:15:25.090 --> 00:15:27.430 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000300
00:15:27.510 --> 00:15:28.970 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Duty is what brought me here.</b></Default>

c0000301
00:15:30.560 --> 00:15:31.850 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You're sure
the portion's the same?</b></Default>

c0000302
00:15:32.640 --> 00:15:34.680 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MAN 5A]
The passage of time is cruel.</b></Default>

c0000303
00:15:35.650 --> 00:15:37.360 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[footsteps approaching]</b></Default>

c0000304
00:15:38.650 --> 00:15:39.650 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hm.</b></Default>

c0000305
00:15:41.270 --> 00:15:42.860 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[STARK] You've got no reason
to glare at me!</b></Default>

c0000306
00:15:42.940 --> 00:15:44.150 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I bought this
with my own money.</b></Default>

c0000307
00:15:45.320 --> 00:15:46.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FERN]
Pardon me.</b></Default>

c0000308
00:15:46.580 --> 00:15:47.740 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>One milk, please.</b></Default>

c0000309
00:15:48.080 --> 00:15:49.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MAN 5A]
Sure thing.</b></Default>

c0000310
00:15:50.870 --> 00:15:52.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[STARK]
So...what?</b></Default>

c0000311
00:15:53.370 --> 00:15:54.490 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You're clearly mad.</b></Default>

c0000312
00:15:55.120 --> 00:15:56.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FERN]
Mister Stark.</b></Default>

c0000313
00:15:56.710 --> 00:15:58.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[STARK] Fine, I guess
you can have half.</b></Default>

c0000314
00:15:58.670 --> 00:16:00.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>This isn't about dessert.</b></Default>

c0000315
00:16:01.130 --> 00:16:04.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What if I told you we're going
be waiting for a long time?</b></Default>

c0000316
00:16:04.500 --> 00:16:05.600 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Two years, even.</b></Default>

c0000317
00:16:06.180 --> 00:16:07.430 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Huh? No, thanks.</b></Default>

c0000318
00:16:07.510 --> 00:16:09.850 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So you and I feel the same way
about it, then!</b></Default>

c0000319
00:16:10.010 --> 00:16:11.010 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[STARK]
Sure?</b></Default>

c0000320
00:16:11.300 --> 00:16:12.300 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What's her deal?</b></Default>

c0000321
00:16:12.430 --> 00:16:13.640 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FERN]
That's a relief.</b></Default>

c0000322
00:16:13.800 --> 00:16:15.810 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You're relatively normal,
at least.</b></Default>

c0000323
00:16:16.230 --> 00:16:17.310 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[STARK]
I-I'm lost.</b></Default>

c0000324
00:16:17.400 --> 00:16:18.770 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Did-Did I do something
to offend you?</b></Default>

c0000325
00:16:21.730 --> 00:16:23.980 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[STARK] So, you wanna find
a way through the checkpoint.</b></Default>

c0000326
00:16:24.940 --> 00:16:27.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Sure. I'll see what I can do.</b></Default>

c0000327
00:16:27.660 --> 00:16:29.070 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Thanks. You won't regret it.</b></Default>

c0000328
00:16:30.160 --> 00:16:31.820 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[STARK]
What if you just flew us up</b></Default>

c0000329
00:16:31.910 --> 00:16:32.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and over the city wall?</b></Default>

c0000330
00:16:34.320 --> 00:16:36.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The wall's only one part
of the problem.</b></Default>

c0000331
00:16:36.540 --> 00:16:38.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>There's a powerful barrier
all around the border</b></Default>

c0000332
00:16:39.000 --> 00:16:41.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>that extends
to the maximum flying height.</b></Default>

c0000333
00:16:41.830 --> 00:16:42.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That makes sense.</b></Default>

c0000334
00:16:43.460 --> 00:16:45.590 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Explains how they keep
the winged monsters out.</b></Default>

c0000335
00:16:46.890 --> 00:16:47.800 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Let's ask around.</b></Default>

c0000336
00:16:48.260 --> 00:16:50.090 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Our first stop should be
the merchant's guild.</b></Default>

c0000337
00:16:50.590 --> 00:16:51.970 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>They must be
trading somewhere.</b></Default>

c0000338
00:16:53.840 --> 00:16:55.510 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000339
00:17:03.270 --> 00:17:04.350 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[water splashing]</b></Default>

c0000340
00:17:04.480 --> 00:17:06.740 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FERN] Trade has been
completely shut down.</b></Default>

c0000341
00:17:07.110 --> 00:17:09.360 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If guarded caravans
aren't allowed through,</b></Default>

c0000342
00:17:09.950 --> 00:17:12.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>things in the northern lands
must be quite serious.</b></Default>

c0000343
00:17:13.950 --> 00:17:15.320 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm afraid
we may need to give up</b></Default>

c0000344
00:17:15.410 --> 00:17:16.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>until things settle down.</b></Default>

c0000345
00:17:18.000 --> 00:17:18.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Not yet.</b></Default>

c0000346
00:17:19.540 --> 00:17:21.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We should ask
around the black market</b></Default>

c0000347
00:17:21.250 --> 00:17:22.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and thieves guild first.</b></Default>

c0000348
00:17:23.170 --> 00:17:24.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Wouldn't that be
a bit dangerous</b></Default>

c0000349
00:17:24.750 --> 00:17:25.680 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>even for us?</b></Default>

c0000350
00:17:25.840 --> 00:17:26.800 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Lucky for you,</b></Default>

c0000351
00:17:27.130 --> 00:17:29.220 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I look tough enough
not to be questioned.</b></Default>

c0000352
00:17:29.590 --> 00:17:31.050 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Plus, I bluff like a pro.</b></Default>

c0000353
00:17:32.260 --> 00:17:34.010 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You do have a thievish face.</b></Default>

c0000354
00:17:34.090 --> 00:17:35.090 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[STARK]
I heard that.</b></Default>

c0000355
00:17:35.510 --> 00:17:37.560 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000356
00:17:53.610 --> 00:17:54.740 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[STARK]
What a waste.</b></Default>

c0000357
00:17:55.790 --> 00:17:57.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's no big surprise.</b></Default>

c0000358
00:17:57.660 --> 00:17:59.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The town's stuck
on the defensive.</b></Default>

c0000359
00:18:00.250 --> 00:18:02.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If they don't open back up,
we're stuck, too.</b></Default>

c0000360
00:18:02.830 --> 00:18:03.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You know...</b></Default>

c0000361
00:18:04.370 --> 00:18:06.090 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>we could always pay
the guard station</b></Default>

c0000362
00:18:06.170 --> 00:18:07.050 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>a quick visit.</b></Default>

c0000363
00:18:09.970 --> 00:18:11.800 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-You good?
-Yes.</b></Default>

c0000364
00:18:12.420 --> 00:18:15.220 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm just a little surprised
by your cooperation is all.</b></Default>

c0000365
00:18:15.810 --> 00:18:17.430 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You said that
you didn't want to wait,</b></Default>

c0000366
00:18:18.140 --> 00:18:19.890 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>so I'm doing all of us a favor.</b></Default>

c0000367
00:18:20.730 --> 00:18:22.980 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You're even more desperate
to leave than I am.</b></Default>

c0000368
00:18:25.900 --> 00:18:28.610 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Well...I don't have
a lot of time.</b></Default>

c0000369
00:18:29.690 --> 00:18:31.150 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That was awfully vague.</b></Default>

c0000370
00:18:31.240 --> 00:18:33.240 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[wind whooshing]</b></Default>

c0000371
00:18:33.320 --> 00:18:35.360 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[STARK]
This view. Nice, isn't it?</b></Default>

c0000372
00:18:35.910 --> 00:18:37.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You can really see
the north side.</b></Default>

c0000373
00:18:38.870 --> 00:18:39.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>When I was little,</b></Default>

c0000374
00:18:40.540 --> 00:18:41.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>my master brought me up here.</b></Default>

c0000375
00:18:42.620 --> 00:18:44.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000376
00:18:44.870 --> 00:18:46.340 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[chuckles]
-[EISEN] We departed</b></Default>

c0000377
00:18:46.420 --> 00:18:49.510 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>for the northern lands
from this very city.</b></Default>

c0000378
00:18:50.630 --> 00:18:52.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Tell me all about it, Master!</b></Default>

c0000379
00:18:52.880 --> 00:18:54.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[laughs]
You want to know?</b></Default>

c0000380
00:18:55.130 --> 00:18:57.520 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>See that trail?
Over yonder?</b></Default>

c0000381
00:18:58.220 --> 00:19:00.600 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[STARK] He hardly
ever spoke about himself,</b></Default>

c0000382
00:19:01.430 --> 00:19:03.430 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but he happily relayed
every detail</b></Default>

c0000383
00:19:03.520 --> 00:19:04.770 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>of the heroes' adventure.</b></Default>

c0000384
00:19:06.230 --> 00:19:07.820 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>He's been around
for a long time,</b></Default>

c0000385
00:19:08.400 --> 00:19:09.730 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and for whatever reason,</b></Default>

c0000386
00:19:10.030 --> 00:19:12.440 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>those ten years mattered
more than all the rest.</b></Default>

c0000387
00:19:14.530 --> 00:19:16.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'll bet the same
is true for Frieren.</b></Default>

c0000388
00:19:18.410 --> 00:19:19.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I wonder.</b></Default>

c0000389
00:19:21.160 --> 00:19:22.240 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[STARK]
He's old now</b></Default>

c0000390
00:19:22.490 --> 00:19:24.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and can't travel
like that anymore.</b></Default>

c0000391
00:19:26.050 --> 00:19:27.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>He sent the two of you
to find me,</b></Default>

c0000392
00:19:27.500 --> 00:19:28.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>so that I could fill his spot.</b></Default>

c0000393
00:19:29.340 --> 00:19:31.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[flag fluttering]
-[STARK] Now it's my turn.</b></Default>

c0000394
00:19:32.630 --> 00:19:33.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'll go on this adventure</b></Default>

c0000395
00:19:34.130 --> 00:19:36.760 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and return with stories
just like the ones he told me.</b></Default>

c0000396
00:19:37.640 --> 00:19:39.100 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If they happen
to be ridiculous,</b></Default>

c0000397
00:19:39.260 --> 00:19:40.310 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>that's all the better.</b></Default>

c0000398
00:19:42.430 --> 00:19:44.930 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's the least I can do
to repay my debt to him.</b></Default>

c0000399
00:19:46.730 --> 00:19:50.150 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If I take too long to get back,
my master will pass on.</b></Default>

c0000400
00:19:51.230 --> 00:19:52.230 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[chuckles]</b></Default>

c0000401
00:19:53.570 --> 00:19:54.610 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FERN]
I see.</b></Default>

c0000402
00:19:54.980 --> 00:19:57.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Then we can't allow ourselves
to get tied up here.</b></Default>

c0000403
00:19:58.280 --> 00:20:01.740 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Nope. But I bet he's still got
plenty of years left.</b></Default>

c0000404
00:20:04.740 --> 00:20:07.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[indistinct chatter]</b></Default>

c0000405
00:20:14.790 --> 00:20:16.220 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FERN] Mistress Frieren?</b></Default>

c0000406
00:20:17.180 --> 00:20:19.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Is there a reason you're
creeping around the city?</b></Default>

c0000407
00:20:19.640 --> 00:20:21.390 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Shh, quiet yourself.</b></Default>

c0000408
00:20:22.390 --> 00:20:23.430 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>They're following me.</b></Default>

c0000409
00:20:28.060 --> 00:20:31.190 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Don't stop. She must be
lurking around here somewhere.</b></Default>

c0000410
00:20:31.980 --> 00:20:32.940 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh, great.</b></Default>

c0000411
00:20:33.060 --> 00:20:34.360 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>How'd you rile 'em up?</b></Default>

c0000412
00:20:34.480 --> 00:20:35.560 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I've no clue.</b></Default>

c0000413
00:20:35.820 --> 00:20:38.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I was happily perusing
a magic shop, when suddenly...</b></Default>

c0000414
00:20:40.280 --> 00:20:41.280 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Huh?</b></Default>

c0000415
00:20:42.780 --> 00:20:44.280 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MALE GUARD CAPTAIN 5A]
I'm so terribly sorry!</b></Default>

c0000416
00:20:44.570 --> 00:20:47.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Please, Miss Frieren.
Forgive my insolence!</b></Default>

c0000417
00:20:48.500 --> 00:20:49.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Okay.</b></Default>

c0000418
00:20:49.830 --> 00:20:52.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I have some concerns about
where this seems to be going.</b></Default>

c0000419
00:20:54.130 --> 00:20:55.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MALE CASTELLAN 6A]
I understand</b></Default>

c0000420
00:20:55.210 --> 00:20:57.640 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>the captain of the guard
was quite rude to you.</b></Default>

c0000421
00:20:58.470 --> 00:21:01.390 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>As the castellan of this city,
I apologize.</b></Default>

c0000422
00:21:02.840 --> 00:21:04.840 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh, uh. It's no issue.</b></Default>

c0000423
00:21:05.090 --> 00:21:06.400 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>He did his
guard-ly duties well,</b></Default>

c0000424
00:21:06.480 --> 00:21:07.440 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>if you ask me.</b></Default>

c0000425
00:21:07.560 --> 00:21:10.400 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>In any case, I'm not
in an enormous hurry, or...</b></Default>

c0000426
00:21:10.480 --> 00:21:11.600 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MALE CASTELLAN 6A]
Am I right to assume</b></Default>

c0000427
00:21:11.690 --> 00:21:14.060 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>that you do plan
to travel north again?</b></Default>

c0000428
00:21:15.350 --> 00:21:16.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>According to our information,</b></Default>

c0000429
00:21:17.200 --> 00:21:19.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>the northern lands
are in constant battle</b></Default>

c0000430
00:21:19.240 --> 00:21:21.320 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>with the remnants
of the Demon King's forces.</b></Default>

c0000431
00:21:21.660 --> 00:21:24.030 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You must be concerned
about their situation.</b></Default>

c0000432
00:21:24.410 --> 00:21:25.320 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>My goodness.</b></Default>

c0000433
00:21:25.700 --> 00:21:27.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>A hero as kind
as she is mighty.</b></Default>

c0000434
00:21:28.790 --> 00:21:30.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The people of the north
will be thrilled</b></Default>

c0000435
00:21:30.460 --> 00:21:31.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to hear of your arrival.</b></Default>

c0000436
00:21:32.210 --> 00:21:35.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And as for our checkpoint,
pass through as you wish.</b></Default>

c0000437
00:21:36.300 --> 00:21:37.300 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[gasps]
-[thudding]</b></Default>

c0000438
00:21:37.380 --> 00:21:39.800 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000439
00:21:40.550 --> 00:21:41.680 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[crowd applauds]</b></Default>

c0000440
00:21:43.930 --> 00:21:44.930 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[indistinct chatter]</b></Default>

c0000441
00:21:48.770 --> 00:21:51.190 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I can't believe
that's really all it took.</b></Default>

c0000442
00:21:51.480 --> 00:21:53.270 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Shouldn't we have told them
who you were</b></Default>

c0000443
00:21:53.350 --> 00:21:54.940 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>from the moment
they turned us away?</b></Default>

c0000444
00:21:56.280 --> 00:21:58.610 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I didn't think there was
any point in alerting them.</b></Default>

c0000445
00:21:59.400 --> 00:22:01.150 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And I wanted to take my time.</b></Default>

c0000446
00:22:01.860 --> 00:22:02.900 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What a commotion.</b></Default>

c0000447
00:22:03.150 --> 00:22:05.110 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>This kind of thing
just isn't for me.</b></Default>

c0000448
00:22:06.290 --> 00:22:08.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Who could feel
comfortable like this?</b></Default>

c0000449
00:22:09.620 --> 00:22:12.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm happy I get to see
a proper send-off.</b></Default>

c0000450
00:22:13.960 --> 00:22:16.970 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[door creaking]</b></Default>

c0000451
00:22:20.510 --> 00:22:21.840 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>This must've been how it was</b></Default>

c0000452
00:22:21.920 --> 00:22:23.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>when my master
left for the north.</b></Default>

c0000453
00:22:25.550 --> 00:22:26.560 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000454
00:22:26.730 --> 00:22:29.640 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[wind whooshing]</b></Default>

c0000455
00:22:29.770 --> 00:22:32.100 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000456
00:22:36.740 --> 00:22:37.780 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN]
That's right.</b></Default>

c0000457
00:22:38.440 --> 00:22:39.400 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[snorts]</b></Default>

c0000458
00:22:39.490 --> 00:22:41.240 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If only I'd had
a little more time</b></Default>

c0000459
00:22:41.320 --> 00:22:43.240 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>for my research.</b></Default>

c0000460
00:22:43.440 --> 00:22:44.610 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FERN]
You need to move on.</b></Default>

c0000461
00:22:45.070 --> 00:22:46.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[STARK] You know we risked
life and limb</b></Default>

c0000462
00:22:46.620 --> 00:22:48.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>trying to get out
of there, right?</b></Default>

c0000463
00:22:48.290 --> 00:22:49.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FERN]
Indeed.</b></Default>

c0000464
00:24:20.460 --> 00:24:22.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[DEMON CHILD 6A] It hurts.
-[GRANAT] He died in battle</b></Default>

c0000465
00:24:22.090 --> 00:24:24.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-against Aura ten years ago.
-The Liberation Festival</b></Default>

c0000466
00:24:24.250 --> 00:24:25.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-is tonight.
-[STARK] Why not speak to them?</b></Default>

c0000467
00:24:25.540 --> 00:24:26.930 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[LUGNER] I'm curious about
that mage. -[FERN] What a pain</b></Default>

c0000468
00:24:27.010 --> 00:24:29.510 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-in the rear. -[EISEN]
It's like a fairy tale.</b></Default>

